Ses deux ttes sentendent mal. Mme en

Quand il a mang tout ce qui tranait sur

After it has eaten up all the food in
its territory, it moves to another
area. Its two heads do not get along.

and compete with each other for food,
they always eat too much.

Whichever head eats more than
the other gets to be the leader.

Sus dos cabezas se llevan fatal, y la que consigue

posizione di comando in base a quale mangia di pi.

While hunting for prey, Zweilous wanders its
territory, its two heads often bickering over
which way to go.

Sein Krper weist immer Narben auf, selbst wenn
es gar nicht gekmpft hat. Die beiden Kpfe
nehmen sich stndig gegenseitig das Futter weg.

Las dos cabezas se disputan la comida con
brutalidad. Por eso siempre est cubierto de
heridas, aunque no haya combatido contra nadie.

Le due teste si rubano il cibo a vicenda.
 sempre ricoperto di ferite, anche se non
ha lottato con nessuno.

Their two heads will fight each other over a
single piece of food. Zweilous are covered in
scars even without battling others.
